    <keyword>DISCARD</keyword>
    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This RFC specifies a standard for the ARPA Internet community.  Hosts on the ARPA Internet that choose to implement a Discard Protocol are expected to adopt and implement this standard.  The Discard service simply throws away any data it receives.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
